    <item>
      <title>麦格理表示，拜登可能会动用石油储备来满足夏季需求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/biden-likely-to-tap-oil-reserve-to-meet-summer-gasoline-demand-macquarie-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拜登政府可能需要从该国的紧急储备中动用石油，以应对汽油价格飙升和夏季驾车季节的通胀担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/biden-likely-to-tap-oil-reserve-to-meet-summer-gasoline-demand-macquarie-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 17:51:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普媒体在令人眼花缭乱的上涨后感受到了引力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-15/trump-media-feels-pull-of-gravity-after-dizzying-run-up-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据彭博社的贝利·利普舒尔茨 (Bailey Lipschultz) 报道，随着投资者重新评估 Truth Social 母公司的前景，特朗普媒体科技集团 (Trump Media &amp; Technology Group Corp.) 较上个月的峰值下跌了约 60%，成交量萎缩，期权成交量也下降。当特朗普的股票禁售期结束时，他仍有望获得巨额发薪日，但与几周前相比要小得多。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-15/trump-media-feels-pull-of-gravity-after-dizzying-run-up-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 17:47:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
